Author: iampieman
Text: My doctor put me on an anti-depressant that causes weight gain and I was terrified but tried it and still lost weight at same rage, but the anti depressant wasn’t working so she upped me to 20mg instead of 10mg and now I’ve barely losing weight, idk if it’s the medication or from my binge last week but I’m still thinking of just stopping them but not telling anyone lmao. So totally feel your pain.
